      "body" : "1) I think it's a pity that Qt doesn't break off long tooltip messages itself. How the hell are we (and translators) supposed to know how wide text gets rendered and what will, and will not run off the screen.\r\n\r\n2) Yes, that was forgotten when it was added.",
